"The user begins with View 1 (Overview) to understand the relationship between CLTV and satisfaction across customer statuses. Brushing selects specific value ranges which filter View 2 (Exploration) showing service-type patterns. Clicking service/age groups in View 2 updates View 3 (Detail) with contract/tenure heatmaps. Selections in View 1 also enable radial analysis of churn reasons in View 4 (Insight) for individual customers."